{"title":"C_STL","uid":"c7326b4c451f518385b418d9140aee06","slug":"C/C_STL","date":"2021-11-02T00:39:04.000Z","updated":"2022-06-11T14:24:15.207Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/C/C_STL.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/C_STL.jpeg","content":"<h1 id=\"模板\"><a href=\"#模板\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模板\"></a>模板</h1><p>排序</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">sort(array.begin(), array.end(), \n    [](vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; a, vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; b)&#123;return a[0]&lt;b[0] || a[0]&#x3D;&#x3D;b[0]&amp;&amp;a[1]&gt;b[1];&#125;\n);<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>二分</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">&#x2F;&#x2F;左mid+1，右mid，得到r为左边界\nint bsearch_1(int l, int r)&#123;\n    while (l &lt; r)    &#123;\n        int mid &#x3D; (l+r)&#x2F;2;\n        if (check(mid)) r &#x3D; mid;\n        else l &#x3D; mid + 1;\n    &#125;\n    return r;\n&#125;\n&#x2F;&#x2F;右mid-1，左mid，得到r为右边界\nint bsearch_2(int l, int r)&#123;\n    while (l &lt; r)    &#123;\n        int mid &#x3D; (l+r+1)&#x2F;2;\n        if (check(mid)) l &#x3D; mid;\n        else r &#x3D; mid - 1;\n    &#125;\n    return r;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>快排”枢轴”思想</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>找第key小的元素，每次舍去枢轴另一侧，复杂度logn</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">int key;\nvoid Qsort(int a[], int l ,int h)&#123;\n  while(l&lt;&#x3D;h)&#123;\n    int pivot &#x3D; Part(a,l,h);\n    if(pivot&#x3D;&#x3D;key) do();\n    else if(pivot&gt;key) r&#x3D;pivot-1;\n    else l&#x3D;pivot+1;\n  &#125;\n&#125;\nint Part(int a[], int l, int h)&#123;\n  int pivot &#x3D; a[l];\n  while(l&lt;h)&#123;\n    while(l&lt;h &amp;&amp; a[h]&gt;&#x3D;pivot) h--;\n    a[l]&#x3D;a[h];\n    while(l&lt;h &amp;&amp; a[l]&lt;&#x3D;pivot) l++;\n    a[h]&#x3D;a[l];\n  &#125;\n  a[l] &#x3D; pivot;\n  return l;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h1 id=\"vector\"><a href=\"#vector\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"vector\"></a>vector</h1><h2 id=\"基本函数实现\"><a href=\"#基本函数实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本函数实现\"></a>基本函数实现</h2><h4 id=\"1-构造函数\"><a href=\"#1-构造函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.构造函数\"></a>1.构造函数</h4><p><strong>vector()</strong> : 创建一个空vector<br><strong>vector(n, x)</strong> : 创建n个元素值均为t<br><strong>vector(begin,end)</strong> : 复制[begin,end)区间内另一个数组的元素到vector中</p>\n<h4 id=\"2-增加函数\"><a href=\"#2-增加函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.增加函数\"></a>2.增加函数</h4><p><strong>void push_back(x)</strong> ： 尾部增加元素X<br><strong>iterator insert(it, x)</strong> : 迭代器指向元素前增加x</p>\n<h4 id=\"3-删除函数\"><a href=\"#3-删除函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.删除函数\"></a>3.删除函数</h4><p><strong>iterator erase(it)</strong> : 删除向量中迭代器指向元素<br><strong>iterator erase(it1,it2)</strong> : 删除向量中[first,last)中元素<br><strong>void pop_back()</strong> : 删除向量中最后一个元素<br><strong>void clear()</strong> : 清空向量中所有元素</p>\n<h4 id=\"4-遍历函数\"><a href=\"#4-遍历函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.遍历函数\"></a>4.遍历函数</h4><p><strong>reference at(pos)</strong> : 返回pos位置元素引用<br><strong>reference front()/back()</strong> : 返回首尾元素引用<br><strong>iterator begin()/end()</strong> : 返回头指针、尾元素下一位置指针<br>reverse_iterator rbegin() : 反向迭代器，指向最后一个元素<br>reverse_iterator rend() : 反向迭代器，指向第一个元素之前的位置</p>\n<h4 id=\"5-判断函数\"><a href=\"#5-判断函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.判断函数\"></a>5.判断函数</h4><p><strong>bool empty()</strong> : 判断是否为空<br><strong>int size()</strong> : 返回元素个数</p>\n<h2 id=\"访问\"><a href=\"#访问\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"访问\"></a>访问</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">40</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nvector<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">v</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>a<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    cout<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span>v<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span><span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nvector<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token double-colon punctuation\">::</span>iterator it<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>it<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>v<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">begin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>it<span class=\"token operator\">!=</span>v<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">end</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>it<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    cout<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>it<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span><span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"二维数组\"><a href=\"#二维数组\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二维数组\"></a>二维数组</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> N<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> M<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//定义二维动态数组5行6列 </span>\nvector<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>vector<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">v</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>N<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token generic-function\"><span class=\"token function\">vector</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>M<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> v<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>j<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>v<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        cout<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span>v<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span><span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h1 id=\"list\"><a href=\"#list\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"list\"></a>list</h1><h2 id=\"常用操作函数\"><a href=\"#常用操作函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常用操作函数\"></a>常用操作函数</h2><p>同vector，此外有</p>\n<p><strong>lst.assign(n, x)</strong> : 赋值n个x<br><strong>lst.merge(lst1)</strong> : lst1合并到lst<br><strong>lst.pop_front()/push_front()</strong> : 在头部删/添加元素<br><strong>lst.remove()</strong> : 从list删除元素<br>lst.remove_if() : 按指定条件删除元素<br><strong>lst.reverse()</strong> : 把list的元素倒转<br><strong>lst.sort()</strong> : 给list排序<br><strong>lst.splice(lst1)</strong> : lst1剪切到lst<br><strong>lst.swap()</strong> : 交换两个list<br><strong>lst.unique()</strong> : 删除list中相邻重复的元素</p>\n<h1 id=\"map\"><a href=\"#map\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"map\"></a>map</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p> map: 自动按Key升序排序</p>\n<p> unorder_map: 哈希存储无序</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义\"></a>定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">map<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>string<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmap<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>string<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> m <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Jim\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Tom\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmap<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>string<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">m1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>m<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmap<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>string<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">m1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">++</span>m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">begin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">end</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"访问-1\"><a href=\"#访问-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"访问\"></a>访问</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">m.at(&quot;Tom&quot;);&#x2F;&#x2F;无则报错\nm[&quot;Tom&quot;];   &#x2F;&#x2F;无则自动添加，类似insert\nm.find(&quot;Tom&quot;) &#x2F;&#x2F;返回迭代器，否则m.end()\n\nfor (auto x: m) &#123;\n    cout&lt;&lt;x.first&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;&lt;&lt;x.second&lt;&lt;endl;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"插入\"><a href=\"#插入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"插入\"></a>插入</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">insert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token generic-function\"><span class=\"token function\">pair</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>string<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"student\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nm1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">insert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">begin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">end</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"删除\"><a href=\"#删除\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除\"></a>删除</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">m.erase(m.find(&quot;Jim&quot;));&#x2F;&#x2F;迭代器删除，返回i下一个迭代器\nm.erase(&quot;Tom&quot;);\t&#x2F;&#x2F;key删除，返回删除元素数目\nm.clear();  &#x2F;&#x2F;清空<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"仅Map\"><a href=\"#仅Map\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"仅Map\"></a>仅Map</h2><p><strong>size_t  count(key)</strong> : 返回key出现的次数0/1</p>\n<p><strong>lower_bound()</strong> : 返回键值&gt;=给定元素的第一个位置</p>\n<p><strong>upper_bound()</strong> : 返回键值&gt;给定元素的第一个位置</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"priority-queue\"><a href=\"#priority-queue\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"priority_queue\"></a>priority_queue</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>维护前k大的序列用小顶堆，第k+1个时队首(最小)出队</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"定义-1\"><a href=\"#定义-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义\"></a>定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">priority_queue&lt;Type, Container, Functional&gt;;\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F;默认大顶堆,容器vector\npriority_queue&lt;int&gt; q;\n&#x2F;&#x2F;小顶堆\npriority_queue &lt;int,vector&lt;int&gt;,greater&lt;int&gt; &gt; q;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"函数\"><a href=\"#函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数\"></a>函数</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">top()\npop()\npush()\nempty()\nsize()<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"比较方式\"><a href=\"#比较方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"比较方式\"></a>比较方式</h2><p>1.重载运算符<code>&quot;&lt;&quot;</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">struct fruit &#123;\n\tstring name;\n\tint price;\n\tfriend bool operator &lt; (fruit f1,fruit f2)&#123;\n\t\treturn f1.peice &lt; f2.price; &#x2F;&#x2F;大顶堆 \n    \treturn f1.peice &gt; f2.price; &#x2F;&#x2F;小顶堆 \n\t&#125;\n&#125;;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>2.仿函数</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">struct cmp&#123;\n\tbool operator()(fruit f1,fruit f2)&#123;\n\t\treturn f1.price &lt; f2.price; &#x2F;&#x2F;大顶堆\n\t\treturn f1.price &gt; f2.price; &#x2F;&#x2F;小顶堆\n\t&#125;\n&#125;;\npriority_queue&lt;fruit,vector&lt;fruit&gt;,cmp&gt; q;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"set\"><a href=\"#set\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"set\"></a>set</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>自动有序、去重</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"自定义排序\"><a href=\"#自定义排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自定义排序\"></a>自定义排序</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">st